 you won’t find those options in this application since its learning tools are digital. For visual references you can download a PDF guidebook that supplements each of the 30 lessons with quizzes that help you understand and absorb the words that are being taught.","There are times when a word like “onerous” or “arduous” expresses a thought more effectively than simply using a more commonplace word such as “difficult.” This vocabulary builder will help you find the right word when you need it. Through repetition and practice, you’ll find yourself thinking of the exact word you need to express what you want to say, whether you’re writing an email or talking with a friend."]},"id":"f3681055-d652-4b28-9384-0f82bfce00b1","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_58488","url":"/overnight-vocabulary-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"aaron-mccarter","url":"/author/aaron-mccarter","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Aaron McCarter","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"EMPGWr9T6iJCifmMZAJCYY","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2013-12-21T00:52:44Z","datePublished":"2013-12-21T00:52:44Z","name":"Overnight Vocabulary","synopsis":"Overnight Vocabulary works on the principle of quality over quantity, which isn’t to say that this vocabulary builder doesn’t have a lot of substance.","review":{"rating":77,"pros":[""],"cons":[""]},"strapline":"Overnight Vocabulary works on the principle of quality over quantity, which isn’t to say that this vocabulary builder doesn’t have a lot of substance.","language":"en","dateModified":"2013-12-21T00:52:44Z","id":"5W5Ffj7woHr56zppDt2B39","meta":{"title":"Overnight Vocabulary Review - Pros, Cons and Verdict","description":"Overnight Vocabulary offers 300 important words for you to learn through daily 15-minute study sessions. See our review."},"products":[{"slug":"overnight-vocabulary","url":"/product/overnight-vocabulary","dateCreated":"2019